                            <comment id="16871649" author="apurtell" created="Mon, 24 Jun 2019 18:18:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After the fix is ready we should also have a unit test that confirms that no files are written outside of where we expect, so we can catch this kind of error in the future. Could be done as part of this work or as a follow up PR and JIRA, but we should have that additional test coverage in place going forward.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
